title: Level Up - Novel Updates
tags: Blind Protagonist   Dungeons   Game Elements   Level System   Male Protagonist   Time Travel
author: Kang Hyun Kim   김강현
description: Having lost both eyes, he has lived his life fighting against others in a dungeon until he died. What kind of secret did he take to his death? And how is it that he opened his eyes to find that not only was he not dead…but he was able to see? Let’s find out. Open your eyes and level up!>
